    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J411">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Color of the Grave is Green --</l>
                    <l>The Outer Grave -- I mean --</l>
                    <l>You would not know it from the Field --</l>
                    <l>Except it own a Stone</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To help the fond -- to find it --</l>
                    <l>Too infinite asleep</l>
                    <l>To stop and tell them where it is --</l>
                    <l>But just a Daisy -- deep --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Color of the Grave is white --</l>
                    <l>The outer Grave -- I mean --</l>
                    <l>You would not know it from the Drifts --</l>
                    <l>In Winter -- till the Sun --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Has furrowed out the Aisles --</l>
                    <l>Then -- higher than the Land</l>
                    <l>The little Dwelling Houses rise</l>
                    <l>Where each -- has left a friend --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Color of the Grave within --</l>
                    <l>The Duplicate -- I mean --</l>
                    <l>Not all the Snows c'd make it white --</l>
                    <l>Not all the Summers -- Green --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>You've seen the Color -- maybe --</l>
                    <l>Upon a Bonnet bound --</l>
                    <l>When that you met it with before --</l>
                    <l>The Ferret -- Cannot find --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
